name: Dupe
description: Dupe is the internet’s most viral shopping hack, try it out! — as seen by millions of shoppers on The Today Show and used my over a million shoppers every month. Dupe gives shoppers more choices by scouring the internet for similar products within seconds. Feels like a treasure hunt and saves shoppers time and money. Brands love Dupe because their otherwise undiscovered products are instantly surfaced to high-intent shoppers in a generative marketplace.
